</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[163,1352,2299,2332]" pageId="23" pageNumber="618" type="breeding">
<paragraph blockId="23.[161,1367,2027,2527]" box="[163,1352,2299,2332]" pageId="23" pageNumber="618">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[163,297,2299,2332]" pageId="23" pageNumber="618">Breeding.</emphasis>
One pregnant Kuznetsov’s Mole collected in September had three fetuses.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[161,810,2337,2370]" pageId="23" pageNumber="618" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="23.[161,1367,2027,2527]" box="[161,810,2337,2370]" pageId="23" pageNumber="618">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[161,396,2337,2370]" pageId="23" pageNumber="618">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Kuznetsov’s Mole is fossorial.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
